These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, soul, trance, rock, punk, indie, salsa
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of punk is between the fan of reggae and the fan of trance##2
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of soul and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | trance | punk | reggae | rock | soul | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, reading, board-games, writing, puzzles, woodworking, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | video-games | singing | board-games | writing | reading | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, board-games, collecting, rock-climbing, chess, camping, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping | chess | board-games | drawing | collecting | rock-climbing |

