4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |   5    |    6    |  7   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing | rugby | water-polo | ice-hockey | handball | climbing |

